abstract: A wave of mergers and acquisitions buoyed the market.
snippet: A wave of mergers and acquisitions buoyed the market.
lead_paragraph: It was another strong week for the stock market, and it ended with the Dow Jones industrial average reaching another record close and the Standard & Poor’s 500-stock index tantalizingly near a record of its own.

headline.main: Another Dow Record, and S.& P. Comes Close
headline.print_headline: Another Dow Record, and S.& P. Comes Close
